'''Abdülkerim Bardakcı''' (born 7 September 1994) is a Turkish professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[centre-back]] for [[Süper Lig]] club [[Galatasaray S.K. (football)|Galatasaray]] and the [[Turkey national football team|Turkey national team]].

==Club career==
Bardakcı made his [[Süper Lig]] debut on 17 August 2013 against [[Fenerbahçe S.K. (football)|Fenerbahçe]].<ref name="TFF.org">{{cite web | url = http://www.tff.org/Default.aspx?pageId=526&kisiId=1048397 | title = ABDÜLKERİM BARDAKCI – Player Details TFF | publisher = TFF.org | accessdate = 16 February 2014}}</ref>

On 25 June 2022, an agreement was reached with Bardakcı and his club [[Konyaspor]] on the transfer of the player.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.galatasaray.org/haber/futbol/abdulkerim-bardakci-galatasaray-da/51173|title=Abdülkerim Bardakcı Galatasaray'da!|publisher=Galatasaray S.K.|date=25 June 2022|access-date=25 June 2022}}</ref> Accordingly, a net transfer fee of €2.8 million would be paid to the former club of the player.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.galatasaray.org/haber/gs-sportif-a-s/profesyonel-futbolcu-abdulkerim-bardakcinin-transferi-hakkinda/51174|title=Profesyonel Futbolcu Abdülkerim Bardakcı'nın transferi hakkında|publisher=Galatasaray S.K.|date=25 June 2022|access-date=25 June 2022}}</ref>

Bardakcı became the champion in the [[Süper Lig]] in the [[2022–23 Süper Lig|2022–23]] season with the [[Galatasaray S.K. (football)|Galatasaray]] team. Defeating [[MKE Ankaragücü|Ankaragücü]] 4–1 away in the match played in the 36th week on 30 May 2023, which secured Galatasaray their 23rd league championship in club history.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/65761517|title=Turkish Super Lig: Galatasaray win title for 23rd time after beating Ankaragucu 4-1|publisher=BBC Sport|date=30 May 2023|access-date=31 May 2023}}</ref>

==International career==
He was named in Turkey's 26-man squad for [[UEFA Euro 2024]].<ref>{{cite news |date=7 June 2024 |title=A Millî Takımımızın EURO 2024 Aday Kadrosu Açıklandı |trans-title=EURO 2024 Candidate Squad of Our National Team Announced |url=https://www.tff.org/default.aspx?pageID=202&ftxtID=44561 |language=tr |publisher=[[Turkish Football Federation]] |access-date=18 June 2024}}</ref>

